          <pre style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Symbol;">Â·</span><span style="font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Calibri','sans-serif';">Please stay up to date by checking your Citadel email, &nbsp;local news sources, the collegeâ€™s <strong><a href="https://www.facebook.com/TheCitadel">Facebook</a></strong> and<strong> <a href="https://twitter.com/TheCitadelOEA">Twitter</a></strong> pages and <a href="http://www.citadel.edu/">citadel.edu</a>. .</span></pre> 
