         <div class="storytitle">
          Citadel System Maintenance
         </div> 
         <div class="storycontent">
           Maintenance of Citadel systems is announced on the portal login page (
          <a href="https://lesesnegateway.citadel.edu/" target="_blank">here</a>) and an ITS web page (
          <a href="http://citadel.edu/root/help-center/maintenance-to-citadel-systems" target="_blank">here</a>). If these pages are not available, please go to 
          <a href="http://www.bulldogalert.info/" target="_blank">www.bulldogalert.info</a> for more information. 
         </div> 
